Package gdi.game

Class WorldObject

java.lang.Object
gdi.game.WorldObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
gdi.game.Drawable
public class WorldObject extends Object
A class that helps managing Objects that need to reference a world. This class stores a reference to a world and provides some basic methods to access the different world types available.
Version:
1.0
Author:
frank
